<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{صَرْصَرٍ}</span>: شَدِيدَةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{عَاتِيَةٍ}</span>: قَالَ ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ: عَتَتْ عَلَى الخُزَّانِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{سَخَّرَهَا عَلَيْهِمْ سَبْعَ لَيَالٍ وَثَمَانِيَةَ أَيَّامٍ حُسُومًا}</span> <span class="c4">[الحاقة: ٧]</span> <span class="c2">«مُتَتَابِعَةً»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{فَتَرَى القَوْمَ فِيهَا صَرْعَى كَأَنَّهُمْ أَعْجَازُ نَخْلٍ خَاوِيَةٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[الحاقة: ٧]</span> <span class="c2">«أُصُولُهَا»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{فَهَلْ تَرَى لَهُمْ مِنْ بَاقِيَةٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[الحاقة: ٨]</span> <span class="c2">«بَقِيَّةٍ»</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>